								<path
									d="M0 12.5C0 15.8152 1.31696 18.9946 3.66117 21.3388C6.00537 23.683 9.18479 25 12.5 25C15.8152 25 18.9946 23.683 21.3388 21.3388C23.683 18.9946 25 15.8152 25 12.5C25 9.18479 23.683 6.00537 21.3388 3.66117C18.9946 1.31696 15.8152 0 12.5 0C9.18479 0 6.00537 1.31696 3.66117 3.66117C1.31696 6.00537 0 9.18479 0 12.5ZM11.7676 18.4082C11.3086 18.8672 10.5664 18.8672 10.1123 18.4082C9.6582 17.9492 9.65332 17.207 10.1123 16.7529L14.3604 12.5049L10.1123 8.25684C9.65332 7.79785 9.65332 7.05566 10.1123 6.60156C10.5713 6.14746 11.3135 6.14258 11.7676 6.60156L16.8457 11.6699C17.3047 12.1289 17.3047 12.8711 16.8457 13.3252L11.7676 18.4082Z"
